Subject: Your FedEx Shipment Notification

Dear [Recipient's Name],

We are pleased to inform you that your package with tracking number 123456789 has been successfully processed and is on its way to you via FedEx. 

Estimated Delivery Date: [insert estimated delivery date]

Please find below the shipment details for your reference:

- Sender: [Sender's Name]
- Destination: [Recipient's Address]
- Weight: [Weight of the Package]
- Service: FedEx Express
- Tracking Number: 123456789

For real-time tracking updates, please visit the FedEx website and enter the tracking number provided above.

If you have any questions or concerns regarding your shipment, please do not hesitate to contact our customer service team at 1-800-123-4567.

Thank you for choosing FedEx for your shipping needs.

Sincerely,
FedEx Team
